divs: Sighting DetailsI took pictures of our house to document the exterior work done by a contractor. I picked one window to photograph because there was no sun shining on it. When the pictures came back there was a strange being and another picture of a white cloudlike sphere. There seems to be somekind of writing on the picture also. I did not see anything the day I took those pictures.I have always felt there is some kind of message in the picture.

Summary: I took a picture and some type of being showed up when it was developed.
